## Limitations

The report is based on available online resources and may not capture the most recent changes in state laws or healthcare policies regarding nurse practitioners. Additionally, the acceptance of NPs as primary care providers can vary significantly by state and healthcare system, which may not be fully reflected in the sources reviewed. Further research, including interviews with healthcare professionals and policymakers, could provide more comprehensive insights.